       </sup>
       towards lower apparent molecular size in SEC and MALLS in the absence of ABA is indicative of equilibrium between monomeric and dimeric forms. PYR1
       <sup>
        H60P
       </sup>
       dissociates completely into monomeric species in the presence of 1 mM ABA (red curve). (
       <strong>
