       <sup>
        H60P
       </sup>
       measured by ITC. Concentrated solutions of both proteins were repeatedly injected into the ITC cell filled with buffer and dissociation thermograms were recorded. The estimated dimer dissociation constant for PYR1
       <sup>
        H60P
       </sup>
       is indicated. (
       <strong>
